"khalis makhan dudh makhany kithy gye" 
some of the lyrics taken from the book "Pani wich madhani" by Abeer Abozari a Punjabi poet. most of the people don't know this fact, I know it bcz my father used to read poems of that book to me and my siblings in our childhood. It was great book indeed. must read it if you love reading like me :)
